Now, let's look at its design.

00:05:35.870 --> 00:05:38.600
A classic, timeless style.

00:05:38.750 --> 00:05:40.430
Quite distinctive.

00:05:41.630 --> 00:05:44.120
The central diamond
and the surrounding smaller diamonds

00:05:44.190 --> 00:05:45.360
complement each other,

00:05:46.000 --> 00:05:47.360
