Why did Song Zhizhi refuse
to accept the ring?

00:13:12.820 --> 00:13:14.380
There's no way she couldn't tell

00:13:15.180 --> 00:13:17.420
that this ring and the rough gemstones
her family has hidden

00:13:18.020 --> 00:13:19.500
are from the same batch.

00:13:20.500 --> 00:13:21.660
If she knew,

00:13:22.700 --> 00:13:23.940
